窽字的汉语字典释义

[①]［kuǎn］
［《廣韻》苦管切，上緩，溪。］
亦作“窽1”。
(1)空隙；洞穴。
(2)空虚。
(3)使空虚。
(4)空乏；贫困。
(5)法，条款。
(6)引申为款式。
(7)象声词。参见“窾坎”。
(8)古水名。
(9)通“款”。古代钟鼎彝器上铸刻的文字。
(10)泛指文件等的款识。

Chinese dictionary definition of words
[①]［kuǎn］
["Guangyun" painstakingly cut, slow up, creek. ]
Also known as "窽1".
(1) Void; cave.
(2) Emptiness.
(3) Make empty.
(4) Vacancy; poverty.
(5) Laws, clauses.
(6) The extension is style.
(7) Onomatopoeia. See "Yikan".
(8) Ancient water names.
(9) Through "section". The characters carved on the ancient bells and dings and Yi wares.
(10) Refers generally to documents, etc.
